### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <replace_with_jwt_token>

### Create transaction with insufficient funds (should return status: FAILED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountId": 2,
  "amount": 999999.00,
  "type": "TRANSFER"
}

### Retry a failed transaction (replace {id} with actual failed transaction ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/1/retry
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all FAILED transactions (admin sees all, user sees only owned)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/status/FAILED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get COMPLETED transactions with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/status/COMPLETED?page=0&size=5&sort=id,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get PENDING transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/status/PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Retry a COMPLETED transaction (expect 409 Conflict)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/1/retry
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
